{
  "texts": [
    "MAILS-meta AI literacy scale 42",
    "MAILS is a general-population scale developed from Ng et al. 's 18 conceptualization of AI literacy with four areas: know and understand AI, use and apply AI, evaluate and create AI, and AI Ethics.",
    "Additionally, it includes further psychological competencies related to the use of AI above the Ng et al. 's 18",
    "areas of AI Literacy-self-efficacy and self-perceived competency.",
    "It is the most extensive instruments out of the reviewed instruments."
  ]
}